name: Baby Shark Universe NFT
description: Within the Baby Shark Universe, you'll discover a mesmerizing underwater realm filled with endless possibilities. Swim alongside Baby Shark and Pinkfong as we explore the deep blue sea. Immerse yourself in this delightful metaverse where imaginations become reality.
